# Vite Environment Variables Example
# Do not put any secrets (passwords, tokens) in this file or any .env file in the frontend.
# The frontend is exposed to the client, so anything starting with VITE_ is public.

# The URL of the FairAC backend API. 
# In development, it automatically falls back to your local IP if this is empty.
# In production, set this to your Oracle Cloud backend URL (e.g., https://api.fairac.com/api/v1)
VITE_API_URL=
